Userspace send msg size is 4byte (read)
Userspace send msg size is header + data(512 bytes) or header + data(36 Kb)  (write)
Userspace recevie msg size is 1bytes, write success.
Userspace receive msg size is header + date (512 bytes) or header + data(36 Kb), read success.

